    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《染色时间》是一款仅由1个人开发的独立游戏。您的支持可以让我走得更远。</h2>《染色时间》灵感来源于经典的日式角色扮演游戏。在游戏中玩家将扮演可以创造出各式各样奇妙溶液的“造物师”少女。通过复杂又有趣的流程制作溶液来满足顾客与委托中的需求。<br>在多个不同游戏模式间进行选择，从传统的剧情模式到Rouge-Lite模式。在不同模式间扮演不同的角色，并体验不同角色各具特色的溶液制作玩法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/cddfb9245a5cc8b7b63953c27f7d56ce.poster.avif?t=1723655789\" width=586 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/cddfb9245a5cc8b7b63953c27f7d56ce.webm?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/cddfb9245a5cc8b7b63953c27f7d56ce.mp4?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索超过100种各具特色的溶液，每种溶液都充满了各式各样的性质。<br></li><li>通过控制变量来使相同的溶液产生不同性质，甚至将性质在不同溶液间转移。<br></li><li>利用20余种技能道具与更多的染色buff协助溶液的制作。<br></li><li>规划布局与专注力消耗，没有良好的规划以及专注力的浪费都可能导致溶液无法达到标准。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/449c674eaf559b8a6ab3e0e52e01372c.poster.avif?t=1723655789\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/449c674eaf559b8a6ab3e0e52e01372c.webm?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/449c674eaf559b8a6ab3e0e52e01372c.mp4?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/eec5c661a0286597d16e4f8446f1eab6.poster.avif?t=1723655789\" width=586 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/eec5c661a0286597d16e4f8446f1eab6.webm?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/eec5c661a0286597d16e4f8446f1eab6.mp4?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>感受轻百合风格人物关系。<br></li><li>与近10位女孩成为朋友。从冷漠的图书管理员到腹黑的青梅竹马，甚至是长着兽耳和尾巴的老奶奶？<br></li><li>与伙伴的交流会逐渐改变你的性格，并反馈在造物过程之中。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/9f93acdd0d690a352c4d57f2541d6c7d.poster.avif?t=1723655789\" width=600 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/9f93acdd0d690a352c4d57f2541d6c7d.webm?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/9f93acdd0d690a352c4d57f2541d6c7d.mp4?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/2f1b1729262e5de73add3ad9b6fbd503.poster.avif?t=1723655789\" width=586 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/2f1b1729262e5de73add3ad9b6fbd503.webm?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/2f1b1729262e5de73add3ad9b6fbd503.mp4?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>接受来自同伴和居民们异想天开的委托，并制作奇奇怪怪的溶液来完成它们。<br></li><li>随着委托深入了解每位伙伴。<br></li><li>完成委托的方式会对故事的发展产生细微影响，甚至改变游戏的结局。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/954c1d245342e11e1835864d21f9cb3e.poster.avif?t=1723655789\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/954c1d245342e11e1835864d21f9cb3e.webm?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852090/extras/954c1d245342e11e1835864d21f9cb3e.mp4?t=1723655789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
